<D>__{i will tell you...}
<A>__{nick put his arm around the man's shoulder and guides him toward a display case.}
<C>__{nick}
<D>__{...the thing is, a hundred and fifty dollars gets you very little in the way of japanese technology.}
<C>__{major jenkins}
<D>__{oh.}
<A>__{they stop at the case. nick points.}
