<D>__{it's for my parents.}
<C>__{nick}
<D>__{your parents?}
<C>__{major jenkins}
<D>__{yes. they live with me...}
<A>__{beth enters the frame. nick doesn't see her.}
<C>__{major jenkins}
<D>__{...and they want japanese.}
<A>__{nick stifles a strange urge to giggle. beth tries to subtly get nick's attention.}
<C>__{major jenkins}
<D>__{is there a problem?}
<C>__{nick}
